wareegga waxbarashada: Talaabooyinka uu CPU raaco si uu u fuliyo hal tilmaam
naqshadaha superscalar: Naqshadaynta CPU oo fulin karta tilmaamo badan saacaddiiba
saadaasha laanta: Farsamada halka CPU-gu isku dayo inuu qiyaaso dariiqa shuruuduhu u socon doono
Northbridge: Chipset (nidaamyadii hore) ee CPU-ga ku xidhay RAM iyo basaska xawaaraha sare leh
southbridge: Chipset (nidaamyadii qadiimka ahaa) ee gacanta ku hayay meelaha gaabinaya iyo I/O
hyperthreading: Tiknoolajiyada u oggolaanaysa hal xudunta CPU inay u muuqato sida koorayaal badan oo macquul ah
khatar: Kumbuyuutar habeeya tilmaamaha hoos u dhaca - Nakhshad CPU oo leh tilmaamo ka fudud
cisc: Tilmaanta Isku-dhafan ee Deji Kombiyuutar - Nakhshad CPU oo leh tilmaamo adag oo adag
simd: Tilmaamaha Hal-ku-dhigga Xogta Badan, Farsamada habaynta xogta si barbar socda
dhismaha yar yar: Faahfaahinta fulinta ee gaarka ah ee jaantuska tilmaamaha CPU
nidaamka on chip ah: Isku dhafka qaybaha kala duwan (CPU, GPU, iwm.) ee hal chip
nidaamka gundhig: Nidaam kombuyuutar oo loogu talagalay hawl gaar ah, oo badanaa ku dhex jira qalab weyn
firmware: Software-ka si joogto ah ugu kaydsan qalabka hardware (sida BIOS)
xad dhaafka: Ku socodsiinta CPU xawaarihiisa ka sarreeya sifooyinkii loogu talagalay
code sixitaanka qaladka: Farsamada lagu ogaado oo lagu saxo khaladaadka RAM-ka
ka baxsan fulinta: Farsamo uu CPU-gu u fuliyo hab-raaca hab-dhaqanka badan
xisaabinta tirada: Mabaadi'da ka faa'iidaysiga makaanikada quantum ee xisaabinta
xisaabinta neuromorphic: Qaab dhismeedka xisaabinta maskaxda ee loo habeeyay hawlaha AI
